---
title: Easy BBQ Pulled Chicken & Loaded Fries with Smoked Cheddar & Slaw
description: Get your loaded fries with pulled chicken in a BBQ sauce right here, right now! We’ve got smokey Cheddar cheese to sprinkle on top and a side of slaw when you cook up these loaded fries tonight.
